            <h4 class="avatar-tiny"><a href="//beta.slashdot.org/~rotenberry" class="author" title="author name and user ID">rotenberry (3487) </a> | about a year ago | <a href="//beta.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=3660149&cid=43484231">(#43484231)</a></h4>
